content: I think I'll try out a relaxing bath and some light stretching this weekend. I've been feeling a bit exhausted lately, and I need to take some time for myself. Speaking of which, I wanted to mention that I had a pretty hectic Wednesday last week - I had a doctor's appointment at 9 am, a conference call at 11 am, and a meeting with a potential client at 2 pm. But I still managed to squeeze in a 30-minute walk around the block to clear my head. It was a crazy day, but I'm glad I made time for some self-care.
